item.description:
On January 14, our Metro West Young Professionals Meet Up group celebrates its 1 year anniversary! It has been a great year with fun events and lots of great people meeting each other and developing friendships. We are going back to the place where it all started one year ago- join us for dinner/drinks at John Harvard's Brewhouse in Shopper's World (Rt. 9) Framingham.

Look forward to seeing you there! If you have any ideas for future meet ups please share them at the event too. Everyone pays for their own food/drink. We will meet in the bar area, then get a table in the dining room.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) near bar. If necessary, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Celebrate 1 Year Anniversary of Your Meet Up Group at John Harvard's, Framingham
